    "For the texts from EudraCT, we took the class in the trial announcement (section E.1.1.2).",
    "For the abstracts, we did not have this information available.",
    "We classified the texts manually by considering the MeSH descriptors that journals had assigned to the abstracts in PubMed or SciELO, and the type of journal where they were published.",
    "Note that this approach is less accurate than the classification of texts from EudratCT.",
